    "The resulting rule(s) are immediately understood by humans and constitute a much more intuitive explanation of the black box decision.",
    "In cases black box models, such rules can help trace the error in the dataset and in the statistics of the dataset (the rules that hold on it) that lead to the wrong decision.",
